// of the tridiagonal structure: eigenvalue ≈ 2·peak for a 2×2 block).
//
// Wait — for an isolated 2×2 block [0,a;-a,0], eigs = ±ia.
// For nearly-isolated blocks: eig ≈ ±i·a where a is the local peak.
// Target: a₁≈14.1, a₃≈21.0, a₅≈25.0, a₇≈30.4, a₉≈32.9 (but we have
// 9 elements, 5 peaks at positions 0,2,4,6,8)
